00:10:02.140 --> 00:10:04.880
and was one of the
factors that led up

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:09.220
to what turned into a divorce.

00:10:09.220 --> 00:10:11.670
NATHAN: My fiancee and I
started having some trouble.

00:10:11.670 --> 00:10:15.880
