LOUIS: I had bad dreams,
panic attacks, anger.

00:10:21.230 --> 00:10:22.640
I had a lot of anger.

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:24.180
ROGER: The anger
that was there--

00:10:24.180 --> 00:10:26.820
anger became my best friend.

00:10:26.820 --> 00:10:28.920
